high_descs: Walk forward and turn left towards the counter
Grab a knife from the counter
Slice the potato on the counter
Walk with the knife towards the small table
Put the knife inside the metal cooking pot
Walk forward and turn left towards the counter
Take a slice of the potato
Walk with the slice of potato towards the preparation table
Put the slice of potato inside the metal cooking pot
Take the metal pot with the slice potato
Walk with the metal cooking pot towards the fridge
Put the metal cooking pot inside the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of potato inside the metal cooking pot put the metal pot inside the fridge

high_descs: Walk straight passed the stove, turn left to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into several slices.
Turn left towards the wooden shelf, turn left towards the kitchen island.
Place the knife in the pan on the island.
Turn around, head towards the shelf, and then turn right towards the sliced potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the potato from the counter.
Turn left towards the shelf and then turn left towards the pan on the counter.
Place the slice of potato into the pan.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Turn right, walk towards the wall, turn left towards the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the pan on the top shelf inside the fridge, close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan with a knife along with a slice of tomato inside the fridge.

high_descs: Go straight, then turn left to face the counter to the right of the oven.
Take the knife from the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn left, go straight to the wooden shelves, turn left, go to the short side of the table to the left.
Put the knife in the pot near the corner of the table.
Turn left, go to the shelves, turn right go back to the counter to the right of the oven.
Take a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn left, go straight to the wooden shelves, turn left, go to the short side of the table to the left.
Put the potato in the pot near the corner of the table.
Take the pot from the table.
Turn right, go to the wall, turn left, go to the fridge ahead.
Put the pot on the bottom shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife, slice of potato in it in the fridge.
